cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.TL, cs.DS, cs.CC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a logical system derived from Linear logic to characterize the set of Polynomial functions. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses a type system for λ-terms in System F. 
- cs.TL (Theoretical Computer Science) is relevant as the paper deals with the expressivity and completeness of the type system. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions the evaluation of λ-terms with polynomial cost. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also a possibility as the paper discusses the poly-time soundness and completeness of the type system.
